<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="31" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Objetivos do neg&oacute;cio</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: Analisa como a lideran&ccedil;a da organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o compreende e define seus objetivos presentes e futuros. Parte da identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do plano estrat&eacute;gico da empresa e das escolhas poss&iacute;veis para incluir a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="31" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o da proposta de valor</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o cria uma ponte entre a proposta de valor atual e a proposta de valor futura, conectando-se com as etapas anteriores.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
