<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="31" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="4" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Apoio da alta gest&atilde;o</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: A lideran&ccedil;a precisa demonstrar abertura a mudan&ccedil;as e erros, al&eacute;m de fornecer estrutura de apoio formal ao desenvolvimento de esfor&ccedil;os inovadores.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
