<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Reflex&otilde;es sobre a Digitaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="32" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Muitas tend&ecirc;ncias futuras, como trabalho remoto e processos &agrave; dist&acirc;ncia, foram reformuladas e antecipadas, assim como tend&ecirc;ncias relacionadas ao e-consumo. &Eacute; importante avaliar como essas tend&ecirc;ncias v&ecirc;m mudando e impactando a empresa.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="32" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Com o aumento das possibilidades, como identificar as constantes mudan&ccedil;as e adaptar-se a elas?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
