</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="33" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Engajamento</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o sobre o envolvimento das &aacute;reas funcionais e n&iacute;veis hier&aacute;rquicos nas iniciativas de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o (quais? como? em qual momento?), e quais outros stakeholders participam dos processos de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o (</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW148329999 BCX8">ex</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: fornecedores, clientes, associa&ccedil;&otilde;es).</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="33" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Capacita&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: Trata da defini&ccedil;&atilde;o dos temas essenciais para que os processos de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o possam ocorrer. Tamb&eacute;m envolve o levantamento de din&acirc;micas, ferramentas e m&eacute;todos de capacita&ccedil;&atilde;o, al&eacute;m de definir quais pessoas devem ser capacitadas.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW148329999 BCX8">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW148329999 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="33" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
