<p class="Paragraph SCXW148329999 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">Software</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW148329999 BCX8">: Defini&ccedil;&atilde;o do software que ajuda a executar e gerir melhor projetos realizados &agrave; dist&acirc;ncia.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW148329999 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
